2004-09-15  Mike FABIAN <mfabian@suse.de>

	* hex2bdf.in: add more properties to the bdf headers:
	ADD_STYLE_NAME, PIXEL_SIZE, POINT_SIZE, RESOLUTION_X,
	RESOLUTION_Y, AVERAGE_WIDTH, _MULE_BASELINE_OFFSET. set
	_MULE_BASELINE_OFFSET to -3 for all efont-unicode fonts to make
	them harmonize better with the ETL-fonts from the GNU
	intlfonts-1.2.1 package.


2003-02-16  Mike FABIAN <mfabian@suse.de>

	* hex2bdf.in: add missing properties to the bdf headers: FOUNDRY,
	FAMILY_NAME, WEIGHT_NAME, SLANT, SETWIDTH_NAME CHARSET_REGISTRY,
	and CHARSET_ENCODING.  This is necessary to make these fonts work
	with Xft2.

